item.title: By: Nazim Hussain

item.description: Flow charts flow of data from one unit to other unit eg an item is sold from shop shop keeper gets money there are two transactions one transaction for flow of item from shop to customer and second flow is money from customer to shop keeper. Flow does not care about profit or loss or any type of calculation but in algorithm we have to care and we adopt the procedure how it will be calculated in algorithm
